Injector/Bumblebee/Manterror:



Injector and Bumblebee both looked to each other, their internal scanners 
picking up weapons fire at their base.

"Let's get into the battle!" Injector yelled, charging forward.

"I don't wanna!" Bumblebee yelled, taking out both of his stinger missile 
launchers, adding power to his feet rockets, flying forward.  Raising both 
weapons, he fired off two stinger missiles from each downwards at KitKat.

---

Injector fired off three stinger missiles from his launcher down at Land Mine.

---

Manterror saw the two flyers, each seventy feet ahead of him, Manterror still 
running.
